<h1>You're Invited!</h1>

<p><%= "Hi #{@friend}," %></p><br/>
<p><%= @host %> has invited you to a movie viewing party!</p><br/>

<h3>Event Details</h3>
<p>Movie: <%= @party.movie_title %></p>
<p>Date: <%= @party.starts_at.strftime("%A, %B %e, %Y") %></p>
<p>Time: <%= @party.starts_at.strftime("%I:%M%P") %></p>
<p>Length: <%= "#{@party.duration / 60} hr #{@party.duration % 60} min" %></p><br/>

<p>Can't wait to see you there!</p><br/>

<p>Your friends at Viewing Party</p>
